page: The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints
message: /* Sources of doctrine */ some brief additions for clarification regarding the contents of "The Book of Mormon." Before the phrase gave an impression that it is a history text, which is partially the claim, the other claim being that the text is a record of religious teachings within the Judeo-Christian belief schema, but separated geographically from the Judeo-Christian traditions for in the Middle East and Europe. This is to show the difference from other indigenous religions in the Americas.
